		<Placemark>
			<name>Vlissingen–Terneuzen / North Sea Port Industrial Hub</name>
			<description>Cross-border Dutch-Belgian port cluster handling chemicals, fertilizers, energy products, dry bulk and offshore logistics.</description>
			<LookAt>
