	<Folder>
		<name>Petrochemical Plants</name>
		<Placemark id="0F1F0F17C93EAF2579A4">
			<name>RAPID refinery + Petrochemical plants</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<li>RAPID = Refinery and Petrochemical Integrated Development<br></li><li>A major project inside <b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Pengerang Integrated Petroleum Complex</span></span> (PIPC)</b><br></li><li><b></b><br></li><li>Operated by <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Petronas</span></span><br></li><li>Processes crude oil into fuels (diesel, jet, gasoline).<br></li><li>Produce chemicals used in plastics<br></li><div><br></div>]]></description>
